OL,3,CHungary elections: What is at stake,
OL,4,Cand why do they matter?
OL,6,FWhile Orban has focused on foreign
OL,7,Fpolicy, Magyar's campaigning has
OL,8,Ffocused on the day-to-day issues
OL,9,Faffecting ordinary Hungarians:
OL,10,FInflation, low wages, public health
OL,11,Fcare, transportation, and corruption.
OL,13,FBut Magyar is no liberal progressive.
OL,14,FHis Tisza party is centre-right, and
OL,15,Fhe has carefully avoided divisive
OL,16,Fissues such as Orban's anti-LGBTQ+
OL,17,Fpolicies, and whether Hungary should
OL,18,Fextend more support to Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/23
